camera.name: Down Camera
camera.pipeline: udpsrc port=9092 caps="application/x-rtp,media=(string)video,clock-rate=(int)90000,encoding-name=(string)H265" ! rtpjitterbuffer latency=0 ! rtph265depay ! h265parse ! avdec_h265 ! videoconvert ! capsfilter caps=video/x-raw

camera.name: Up Camera
camera.pipeline: udpsrc port=9090 caps="application/x-rtp,media=(string)video,clock-rate=(int)90000,encoding-name=(string)H265" ! rtpjitterbuffer latency=0 ! rtph265depay ! h265parse ! avdec_h265 ! videoconvert ! capsfilter caps=video/x-raw

driver.name: GcodeDriver
driver.detected-firmware: FIRMWARE_NAME:Smoothieware, X-SOURCE_CODE_URL:best-for-pnp, FIRMWARE_VERSION:Arkver, X-AXES:6, X-PAXES:6, X-GRBL_MODE:0

command.text: M400 ; Wait for moves to complete before returning
{True:M800 T1 P0 S1}{False:M800 T1 P0 S0}
{True:M800 T1 P2 S1}{False:M800 T1 P2 S0}
